<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="he" dir="rtl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>מסלול — תוכנה לניהול ושיבוץ טכנאים לעסקים קטנים</title>
<meta name="description" content="מסלול מחליפה את הוואטסאפ וגוגל שיטס. שיבוץ אוטומטי חכם לטכנאים, מתקינים ועובדי שטח. ניהול קריאות, יומן יומי ומספר שיבוץ לכל קריאה. מתאים לעסקים עם 2-20 טכנאים.">
<meta name="keywords" content="ניהול טכנאים, שיבוץ טכנאים, תוכנה לעסקים קטנים, ניהול קריאות שירות, שיבוץ אוטומטי, ניהול עובדי שטח, תוכנה למתקינים, יומן טכנאים, ניהול שטח, תוכנה לשיבוץ עובדים">
<meta property="og:title" content="מסלול — שיבוץ טכנאים חכם לעסקים קטנים">
<meta property="og:description" content="בדקות — לא בשעות. מסלול מחשבת למי לשלוח, מתי, ולמה.">
<meta property="og:type" content="website">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Heebo:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

:root {
  --navy: #0A1628;
  --navy-2: #0F2040;
  --blue: #2563EB;
  --blue-bright: #3B82F6;
  --blue-glow: rgba(37,99,235,0.25);
  --teal: #0891B2;
  --green: #10B981;
  --amber: #F59E0B;
  --white: #FFFFFF;
  --off: #F0F4FF;
  --gray: #94A3B8;
  --light: #E2E8F0;
}

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

body {
  font-family: 'Heebo', sans-serif;
  background: var(--navy);
  color: var(--white);
  direction: rtl;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* ── NOISE OVERLAY ── */
body::before {
  content: '';
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.035'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 0;
  opacity: 0.4;
}

/* ── GRID PATTERN ── */
.grid-bg {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(37,99,235,0.06) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(37,99,235,0.06) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 60px 60px;
  mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 0%, black 0%, transparent 100%);
}

/* ── NAV ── */
nav {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  z-index: 100;
  padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  background: rgba(10,22,40,0.85);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
}
.nav-logo {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
}
.nav-logo span { color: var(--blue-bright); }
.nav-cta {
  background: var(--blue);
  color: white;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 8px 20px;
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-family: 'Heebo', sans-serif;
  transition: all 0.15s;
  text-decoration: none;
  display: inline-block;
}
.nav-cta:hover { background: #1D4ED8; transform: translateY(-1px); }

/* ── HERO ── */
.hero {
  position: relative;
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 8rem 2rem 6rem;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.hero-glow {
  position: absolute;
  width: 600px;
  height: 600px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(37,99,235,0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 820px; }

.hero-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  background: rgba(37,99,235,0.15);
  border: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.4);
  border-radius: 30px;
  padding: 6px 16px;
  font-size: 0.8125rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #93C5FD;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both;
}
.badge-dot {
  width: 6px; height: 6px;
  background: var(--green);
  border-radius: 50%;
  animation: pulse 2s infinite;
}
@keyframes pulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
  50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(1.3); }
}

.hero h1 {
  font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.1s both;
}
.hero h1 em {
  font-style: italic;
  color: #93C5FD;
}
.hero-sub {
  font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
  color: var(--gray);
  line-height: 1.7;
  max-width: 580px;
  margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
  animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.2s both;
  font-weight: 400;
}
.hero-actions {
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.3s both;
}
.btn-primary {
  background: var(--blue);
  color: white;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 14px 28px;
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-family: 'Heebo', sans-serif;
  transition: all 0.15s;
  box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(37,99,235,0.4);
}
.btn-primary:hover { background: #1D4ED8; transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(37,99,235,0.5); }
.btn-secondary {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  color: white;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 14px 28px;
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-family: 'Heebo', sans-serif;
  transition: all 0.15s;
}
.btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }

.hero-stats {
  display: flex;
  gap: 2rem;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-top: 3rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.4s both;
}
.hero-stat { text-align: center; }
.hero-stat-num {
  font-size: 1.75rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: white;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
  display: block;
}
.hero-stat-lbl { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--gray); }

@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* ── APP PREVIEW ── */
.preview-section {
  position: relative;
  padding: 0 2rem 6rem;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
}
.app-window {
  max-width: 860px;
  width: 100%;
  background: rgba(15,32,64,0.8);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  border-radius: 16px;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 40px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  position: relative;
  animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.5s both;
}
.window-bar {
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  padding: 12px 16px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
}
.dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; }
.dot-red { background: #FF5F57; }
.dot-yellow { background: #FFBD2E; }
.dot-green { background: #28CA42; }
.window-title { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--gray); margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; }
.app-preview-body { padding: 1.5rem; }

/* MOCK DISPATCH UI */
.mock-header { font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 800; color: #64748B; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.mock-search-row { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.mock-input { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 8px; padding: 8px 12px; font-size: 0.8125rem; color: #94A3B8; flex: 1; min-width: 120px; }
.mock-btn-find { background: var(--blue); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 8px; padding: 8px 18px; font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: default; font-family: 'Heebo', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; }
.mock-cats { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom:14px; }
.mock-cat { padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: #94A3B8; }
.mock-cat.active { border-color: var(--blue); background: rgba(37,99,235,0.15); color: #93C5FD; }
.mock-date-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 8px; margin-top: 12px; }
.mock-date-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px; text-align: center; }
.mock-date-card.best { border-color: var(--blue); background: rgba(37,99,235,0.1); }
.mock-dc-merge { font-size: 0.6rem; color: var(--green); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 3px; }
.mock-dc-day { font-size: 0.65rem; color: #64748B; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
.mock-dc-date { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 900; color: white; margin: 2px 0; }
.mock-dc-tech { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #93C5FD; font-weight: 600; }

/* ── PAIN SECTION ── */
.pain-section {
  padding: 6rem 2rem;
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.section-label {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: #3B82F6;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.section-title {
  font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.section-title em { font-style: italic; color: #93C5FD; }
.section-sub { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 560px; }

.pain-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
  gap: 16px;
  margin-top: 3rem;
}
.pain-card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 1.5rem;
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
}
.pain-card:hover { border-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.4); }
.pain-icon { font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 12px; display: block; }
.pain-title { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.pain-desc { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6; }

/* ── HOW IT WORKS ── */
.how-section {
  padding: 6rem 2rem;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
}
.how-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
.steps-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
  gap: 20px;
  margin-top: 3rem;
}
.step-card {
  position: relative;
  padding: 1.5rem;
}
.step-num {
  width: 40px; height: 40px;
  background: rgba(37,99,235,0.15);
  border: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.4);
  border-radius: 10px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: #93C5FD;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.step-title { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.step-desc { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6; }
.step-time {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 8px;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--green);
  background: rgba(16,185,129,0.1);
  border-radius: 4px;
  padding: 2px 8px;
}

/* ── FEATURES ── */
.features-section {
  padding: 6rem 2rem;
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.features-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: 20px;
  margin-top: 3rem;
}
.feature-card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 1.5rem;
  display: flex;
  gap: 14px;
  transition: all 0.2s;
}
.feature-card:hover { border-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.4); background: rgba(37,99,235,0.05); }
.feature-icon-wrap {
  width: 44px; height: 44px; flex-shrink: 0;
  background: rgba(37,99,235,0.12);
  border-radius: 10px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 1.25rem;
}
.feature-title { font-size: 0.9375rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.feature-desc { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6; }

/* ── WHO IT'S FOR ── */
.for-section {
  padding: 6rem 2rem;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
}
.for-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
.for-grid {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 10px;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-top: 2.5rem;
}
.for-tag {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  border-radius: 30px;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  font-size: 0.9375rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  transition: all 0.15s;
}
.for-tag:hover { border-color: var(--blue); background: rgba(37,99,235,0.1); color: #93C5FD; }

/* ── LEAD FORM ── */
.form-section {
  padding: 6rem 2rem;
  max-width: 640px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
}
.form-card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 2.5rem;
  margin-top: 2.5rem;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.form-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
  width: 60%; height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(59,130,246,0.6), transparent);
}
.form-group { margin-bottom: 1rem; text-align: right; }
.form-label { display: block; font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 700; color: #CBD5E1; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.form-input {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 11px 14px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  border-radius: 10px;
  font-size: 0.9375rem;
  font-family: 'Heebo', sans-serif;
  color: white;
  transition: border-color 0.15s;
  outline: none;
}
.form-input:focus { border-color: var(--blue); box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(37,99,235,0.15); }
.form-input::placeholder { color: #475569; }
.form-select {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 11px 14px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  border-radius: 10px;
  font-size: 0.9375rem;
  font-family: 'Heebo', sans-serif;
  color: white;
  outline: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  -webkit-appearance: none;
}
.form-select option { background: #0F2040; color: white; }
.submit-btn {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 14px;
  background: var(--blue);
  color: white;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 10px;
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-family: 'Heebo', sans-serif;
  margin-top: 8px;
  transition: all 0.15s;
  box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(37,99,235,0.35);
}
.submit-btn:hover { background: #1D4ED8; box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(37,99,235,0.5); }
.form-note { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #475569; margin-top: 10px; }

/* SUCCESS */
.form-success {
  display: none;
  padding: 2rem;
  text-align: center;
}
.success-circle {
  width: 64px; height: 64px;
  background: rgba(16,185,129,0.15);
  border: 2px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.4);
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  margin: 0 auto 1rem;
}
.success-title { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.success-sub { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--gray); }

/* ── FOOTER ── */
footer {
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  padding: 2rem;
  text-align: center;
}
.footer-logo { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -0.5px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.footer-logo span { color: var(--blue-bright); }
.footer-text { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: #475569; }

/* ── SCROLL REVEAL ── */
.reveal {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(30px);
  transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
}
.reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

@media(max-width: 640px) {
  nav { padding: 1rem; }
  .hero { padding: 7rem 1.25rem 4rem; }
  .hero h1 { font-size: 2.25rem; }
  .mock-date-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .hero-stats { gap: 1.25rem; }
  .form-card { padding: 1.5rem; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo"><span>מס</span>לול</div>
  <a class="nav-cta" href="#lead-form">הצטרף לפיילוט</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="grid-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge">
      <span class="badge-dot"></span>
      פתוח לעסקים מובילים — גרסת פיילוט
    </div>
    <h1>
      שיבוץ טכנאים<br>
      <em>בשניות, לא בשעות</em>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      מסלול מחליפה את הוואטסאפ וגוגל שיטס. המתאמת מזינה עיר וסוג קריאה — המערכת מחשבת מי הטכנאי, מתי, ולמה.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <button class="btn-primary" onclick="document.getElementById('lead-form').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">
        התחל פיילוט חינמי ←
      </button>
      <button class="btn-secondary" onclick="document.getElementById('how').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">
        איך זה עובד?
      </button>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <span class="hero-stat-num">30 שנ'</span>
        <span class="hero-stat-lbl">מקריאה לשיבוץ</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <span class="hero-stat-num">2–20</span>
        <span class="hero-stat-lbl">טכנאים בעסק</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <span class="hero-stat-num">0 ₪</span>
        <span class="hero-stat-lbl">לחודש הראשון</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- APP PREVIEW -->
<section class="preview-section">
  <div class="app-window reveal">
    <div class="window-bar">
      <div class="dot dot-red"></div>
      <div class="dot dot-yellow"></div>
      <div class="dot dot-green"></div>
      <span class="window-title">מסלול — שיבוץ קריאה</span>
    </div>
    <div class="app-preview-body">
      <div class="mock-header">קריאה חדשה</div>
      <div class="mock-cats">
        <div class="mock-cat active">טוחן אשפה</div>
        <div class="mock-cat">מערכת מים</div>
        <div class="mock-cat">מרכך אבנית</div>
        <div class="mock-cat">קריאת שירות</div>
      </div>
      <div class="mock-search-row">
